f? shouldn&#39;t the others work too? </TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#A6B2F3><font class="bfont"><B>Law</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#A6B2F3><font class="bfont">No...<br>
